Package: dHRUM
Type: Package
Title: dHRUM - distributed Hydrological Response Units Model
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Petr Maca, Eleni Mickovska, Martin Hermanovsky,
Maintainer: Petr Maca <maca@fzp.czu.cz>
Description: The R interface to dHRUM - distributed Hydrological Response Units Model.
    It initializes dHRUM with given number of single HRUs with known IDs and areas, 
    enable to set inputs and parameters to all single HRUs, 
    run dHRU model, gather data on states and fluxes spatially averaged for the catchment
    from all single HRUs. DHRUM enables to select soil storage types, groundwater models on HRU, usrface retention modles,
    and interception models.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
